pandoc 
  to: html
  output-file: people.html
  standalone: true
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  css:
    - ../styles.css
  toc: false
  variables: {}
  
metadata
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: en
  collections:
    ind_profiles:
      output: false
  editor: visual
  theme:
    - cosmo
  title: People
  listing:
    type: grid
    contents: ind_profiles
    sort: name
    fields:
      - image
      - name
      - research
    grid-columns: 4
    image-height: 160px
    page-size: 0
